AutoreplyDescriptionMessage:
When someone likes your profile, the bot sends a previously recorded video, voice or text message. 

This facilitates the immediate start of communication, creating the opportunity for more interesting and personal conversations. 

This way, users can start communicating right here and now, deepening their interactions.

OceanDescriptionMessage:
Would you like to use the functionality of OCEAN+?

\n--->> OCEAN+ is a system of psychological tests that will select you a partner based on your psychological portrait.

O - Openness to Experience
C - Conscientiousness
E - Extraversion
A - Agreeableness
N - Neuroticism
+ - Temperament
"+" Our personal refinement of this test system)

Take one basic test from this list in order to have an improved result OR take an express test.

Express test will take less time, but 6 basic tests will show more accurate results

We recommend that you first pass the express test
